      "content": "i know there's help available, i've heard it all before. but it doesn't change the fact that the version of me that actually had value is just gone. i can't just \"navigate\" through this when the person who was supposed to do all that work doesn't even exist anymore. it's like looking at an empty shell. how am i supposed to just keep going when there's nothing left to keep going for?",
