      "content": "it just feels so hollow. like, you say people care about \"me,\" but what \"me\" is there? the one that failed, the one that's just a disappointment... that person isn't worth anything. it's like being a ghost in my own life. if the soul of who i was is gone, what's the point in the body just... sitting here taking up space? it feels more like a burden than a life.",
